Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.

Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:38.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should understand by seeing my ears and tail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,what an amazing wolf I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:47.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears can overhear incoming disasters,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and differentiate between lies and truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:52.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have saved many of my companions from peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:56.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When people speak of Horo the Wise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It is none other than myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:15.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some fleas in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:18.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fur is of the highest grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:28.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have good judgment if you can see the greatness of my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon be clean, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:40.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from the top of your scalp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:47.12,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Distant Past
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:53.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us thank God for this encounter today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, but who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my wife. She has some burns on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:04.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come see you after I have a look at our soaked luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:28.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We're quite soaked, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}burns{\i0} have cooled off thanks to the cold rain, and it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, what should we do with the wheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do with it? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:46.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Basically, should we thresh it? Or leave it as it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:50.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's only if you actually did dwell in that wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:55.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,As long I live, it will neither rot nor whither.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:04:00.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were eaten, burnt, or mashed, and then returned to the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I might disappear, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be no problem with threshing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:09.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put the wheat grains into a pouch later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably want to carry it yourself, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:15.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be helpful, and even more useful if I could hang it around my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be okay if I left some wheat behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try and sell it in another land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:30.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll grow well because it came from that land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll immediately whither away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, such a thing is pointless because it'll just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:42.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were in the rain for so long, you still stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:51.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to keep a clean aspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it hasn't really hindered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:00.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think that beard of yours is nice, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'd like it more if it were a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you try growing a beard like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other people here, so don't expose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:25.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise; I've always been traveling in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite an insincere idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To hide my face because it is {\i1}burned{\i0}, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:40.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Those burns are proof of who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:44.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like these ears and this tail, I'll believe that it's my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:56.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you came from Yorentsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I stocked up on salt over there and then delivered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I got marten pelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:07.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't you have to return to Yorentsu again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A merchant's wisdom plays its hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:17.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't pay for the salt I buy from a company in Yorentsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I sell the same amount of wheat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,to a branch from the same company in another city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for not receiving a fee for the wheat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to pay for the salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:33.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, I can fulfill both contracts without exchanging any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's quite fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:42.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This system is called bartering, and was invented by merchants to deal with various regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:46.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I own a vineyard in the city of Perentso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:50.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never received payment in such a curious method before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I be bartering instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:07:01.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I am simply able to evade the danger of having my precious money stolen on long journeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:07.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You two own a vineyard, so you only need to look out for hassling merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a dispute over that every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd assume so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You said your name was Lawrence, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:21.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ever in the vicinity of Perentso, please come and visit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife is a bit tired, so please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,May God allow us to meet once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a normal merchant you can find anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:59.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I've had my eyes on that old couple for a while, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't find the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you pulled it off so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:09.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first started out, all merchants seemed like monsters to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Over half of them still seem like monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Zeiren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just started out, but nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And who is your companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A merchant couple, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:38.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You must value her a lot, covering her in such a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting you here is also God's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind letting me have a look at her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:47.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The most enticing time of a journey is in its preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing a dog howl is most dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:58.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To see a woman's back is the most beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:02.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're too carefree and reckless, your dreams will vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do something like that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife is pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She does her best in order to avoid a scolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting you two is truly the working of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:24.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, boss? Would you listen to my story?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes covered with... This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Goat cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I attached a leather strap to it so that you can hang it around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've got to have some of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:04.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:08.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It cost quite a bit to buy the leather strap, the wheat pouch, the goat cheese,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:10.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that, the donation to the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You better prepare yourself for the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you have to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:29.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Vegetables grown by humans are much better than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I also like the concept of cooking food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:33.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat that all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:45.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Human throats are so narrow, it's terribly inconvenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so, since wolves swallow things whole. {you know what else she swallows..}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:51.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, that's because we don't have cheeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't chew at our leisure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:59.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I've choked on potatoes in the past, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like potatoes and I just don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you could differentiate between lies and truth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:18.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How well can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you didn't intend it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:28.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell that you weren't fully truthful when you complimented my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a hundred percent accurate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, believing me or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say I believe you, and now ask you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,could you tell whether that youngster was lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Youngster?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy who approached us in front of the fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:49.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you both look like youngsters to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you're a bit more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That youngster's story, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:07.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor that the silver coin in circulation now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,will be replaced by one with a higher silver content.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you exchange the new coin to another country's currency,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you can exchange it for more than it is worth now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:18.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:21.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we'll collect silver coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:24.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,exchange them when the new one is issued,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll make a profit in the exchange difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:29.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for telling you which coin it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:37.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll share the profit you make with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:43.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell which part it was exactly, but that story was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:46.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not unusual since coins have been introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know why he is lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:55.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When one lies, the subject is not important,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but instead, {\i1}why{\i0} that person lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:04.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years do you think it took me to realize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a youngster, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what would you have done were I not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd put aside whether it was a lie or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:24.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and act as if I believed in his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:26.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:30.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were true, I would gain a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:30.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It would mean someone is scheming something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could find out what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,it would lead to a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I told you that story was a lie, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't hesitant from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You would've accepted either way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:58.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived many times longer than you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's she...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,May my husband's spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Become fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They've become quite powerful, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The church has always been powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:39.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, they weren't as eminent when I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:43.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, it was not so overdone as to say there is only one truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and that people are simply borrowing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:52.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature is not something someone could create.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:58.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've even been wondering when the church started using me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's leave that aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess everything is changing to reflect the era.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, things will really change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever change?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:24.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your homeland hasn't changed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To be comforted by you is a disgrace to the title of "Wise."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry up and come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! You'll accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I won't pay the deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything unless I exchange my pelts for coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:04.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let us meet in a southern town called Pattsio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:07.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When you arrive at Pattsio, stop by a bar named Yorrend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to find me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Yorrend, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yorrend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:17.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a great day too, madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't he be coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The road is muddy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:29.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking on foot is a lot faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:32.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to make him join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Merchants certainly are particular about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an interesting saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:41.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we have more time, we can gain that much more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been observing the peasants for hundreds of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't you think they're precise with time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:57.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not precise with time, but with their surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:02.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:08.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They wake up at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Plow the fields in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:13.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome the new buds in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:16.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the growth in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:19.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate the harvest in autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait for spring in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:24.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't worry about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:30.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're smart, but you lack experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:43.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You become a better person as you grow older.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How many hundreds of years old is that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:57.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your head is probably too old, and mold has built up inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:04.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why we wolves attack people in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:04.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:10.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We eat their heads and try to obtain their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still too young!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not up to my level yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:26.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been attacked in the forest before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,About eight times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was tough, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been able to deal with stray dogs, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolves are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:48.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because they kill many humans in order to obtain-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:54.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I said that your brain had a buildup of mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:57.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So please... Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:50.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolves live in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogs live with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:56.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the difference in their toughness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:01.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolves only know how to hunt for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's how they deal with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we then think to ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:11.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When humans enter the forest, how should we react?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:19.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've attacked humans too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have things I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:29.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're even!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:59.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The worlds that you and I live in are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:19.95,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:25.33,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:30.51,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:33.25,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:35.81,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.24,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:46.57,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:51.91,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:54.54,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:57.60,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:02.56,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:07.65,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.22,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:13.66,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:17.52,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.87,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:23.16,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:29.05,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:32.70,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Business Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:48.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Business Sense.
